{"tid":2388763,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"Priti Patel 嘅 BNO announcement 需要大家幫手 like/comment","createTime":"2021-01-31T11:17:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T12:02:17.000Z","uid":360621,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5dbbc6c4110f0d9e9451b67a2a4f9653f32ea7e7","tid":2388763,"uid":360621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:17:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/pritipatel/status/1355816494089777154?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpritipatel%2Fstatus%2F1355816494089777154%3Fs%3D20&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWoaGsx%2BcvHJ2yW7UCA6IqyI%3D&h=6e060633\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpritipatel%2Fstatus%2F1355816494089777154%3Fs%3D20&h=79ba850c\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/pritipatel/status/1355816494089777154?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\n內政大臣 Priti Patel 宣佈 BNO passport 開放登記嘅 post，<br />\n有啲反移民嘅人圍攻<br />\n不過更仆街嘅係，你會見到啲明顯係 5毛 嘅 acc 扮英國人推波助瀾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家喺時候去twitter戰線，除咗多謝<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">更重要係盡量 like d 正面嘅 comment</span><br />\n將正面嘅 tweet 推上去<br />\n同埋 port 9 d 5毛 post<br />\n<br />\n依家有幾個負面 post 因為多 like 而浮面，當地冇乜留意嘅人睇到會以為反對嘅人為主 <br />\n（不過琴日新聞其實 poll 過，支持嘅人都好多）<br />\n唔想俾少數 targeted + 5毛推波助瀾 嘅 tweet 影響民意<br />\n就幫手多啲 like 正面 comment <br />\n<br />\n英國見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b9dd954cf7ca110ca9d63ec65a4d625677b48ba","tid":2388763,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgm